<br>
As a general rule I think Open Raids are a good thing.  It's a good way to meet people and do other things.  I also feel those holding such events should post them in this forum with a signup sheet.  A lot of people don't look at the calendar in any detail, and thus wouldn't know that Sterm and others are holding open raids that they could attend.<br>
<br>
I think raids like this would have a lot of appeal to the smaller guilds whose members would not otherwise normally be able to go.  IMO this is the single most important reason people gravitate from small guilds to large ones - they feel that if they stay with their smaller guild they will never see the planes.<br>
<br>
